title: Suki Kirai wa Iwanai yo
original_name: 好き嫌いは言わないよ
sinopse:
A sports-minded guy finds himself attracted to his upperclassman, a member of the food club, even though he is not his type. One day, he catches his upperclassman and an unknown man in an erotic situation.

(Source: ANN)

Included one-shot:
Chicchaku tatte Ichininmae
